  "time_ut": 1659272978,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0daf\u0dbb\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db1\u0dd0\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0db8\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dc4\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dd4\u0da7 \u0d9c\u0dd9\u0daf\u0dbb \u0dba\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dd0\u0dba\u0dd2 \u0d9a\u0dd3\u0db8 \u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0dba \u0db1\u0dcf\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd3\u0db8\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Telling a homeless man to go home is a waste of time",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe said that he has no home to go to even though he went to a demonstration saying that Ranil will not go home.",
        "The President also said that there is no point in marching for a homeless man to go home, so please don't waste your time doing such things.",
        "Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe said this while addressing the members of the United National Party and Podujana Peramuna, former local government representatives and seat organizers in Kandy district.",
        "\"If you guys are ready, bring a big crowd. Build my house within six months. Build the house and tell Ranil to come and go to Ranil's house after I move there. Build the village or build my house. Do one of the two. Otherwise, tell Ranil to go to the house. \"No,\" the president said."
      ],
